data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS have completely upgraded this home in Reflection Lake. Situated on a large corner lot with fenced back yard. Renovated kitchen with maple cabinets and granite c-tops. Family room w/ wood burning fpl & access to patio. Spacious formal LR/DR w/ fresh paint and new flooring. Upper level features all new carpet. Master suite w/ upd. bath. 1/4 mile to future metro!
